    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/credibility-assessment-team-depuy",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted because the single ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration represents the most critical and regulatory-standard loading scenario. All QoI comparisons satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and <10% relative error bounds. The FEA model is deemed credible for its intended use in the 510(k) submission.",
